    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <h3>Is ChatGPT better than Microsoft Copilot?</h3>
    <p>It depends on your specific use case. ChatGPT is the better standalone AI assistant for writing, coding, and creative work. Consider your primary workflow needs.</p>
    <h3>Which is more affordable?</h3>
    <p>Both offer competitive pricing with free and paid tiers. Compare the features that matter for your workflow.</p>
    <h3>Can I use both together?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Many professionals use both tools together, leveraging each for its strengths in different workflows.</p>
    <h3>Which has better integrations?</h3>
    <p>Both integrate with popular tools. The best choice depends on which ecosystem you already use.</p>
  </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
